name: Chupa COW bra
description:
CHUPA COW BRA

Fly around with your saucer and try to save the cows from the meatgrinder.

Use your flying skills to position your ship on top of the cows and abduct them so the carnivore humans don`t kill them. xD

Hello, my name is Nev32, and this is my first ever game.I have spent many years as an Industrial Designer and Architectural Designer, but the future in games seems much more interesting

I will improve this page soon enough, for now, is just a test, an experiment to see if my gamedev skills cut and, maybe, try to get a job with it as well
